question - https://www.codewars.com/kata/57e0206335e198f82b00001d/train/python

solution 

def esrever(st):
    lst = []
    st = list(st)
    
    for index in range(len(st) - 1):
        lst.append(st[index])    
    
    if len(st) > 0:
        return ''.join(lst[::-1]) + st[-1]
    else: 
        return ''.join(lst[::-1])
